Premier Foods of South Africa Plans Acquisitions, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-07-19T05:13:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/premier-foods-of-south-africa-plans-acquisitions-business-day-reports.html
Premier Foods Ltd. of  South Africa 
plans to make acquisitions and to expand into other South
African countries, Johannesburg’s Business Day newspaper
reported, citing Ian Visser, the company’s chief executive
officer.  The company plans to spend 500 million rand ($72 million)
on expanding current facilities, mainly its baking unit, the
newspaper said, citing Visser.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  